<h2 style="color:#667799;font-family:'Courier New', verdana;font-size: 23px;">Fonts</h2>
<p style="font-size:13px;font-family:'Courier New', verdana;color:#ffa500;">Use only standard font names. Electronic mail does not display custom fonts well. Specify <code style="font-family:monospace;background-color:#808080;">font_size</code> in pixels only.</p>
<h2 style="color:#667799;font-family:'Courier New', verdana;font-size: 23px;">Colors</h2>
